search_title: Ndapota izvinyororwe zvako, muenzaniso wako wemakasitumwa kana iyo yako iimeyili uye uyendepiwoe zvinyororomero.
search_input_placeholder: Ndapota entererera neTracking Number, Order Number kana iyo yako Imeyili
description_no_info: Mafuramu ematengeni akatungamira, asi pacakidhi harina kupinda mujeri neruzha.
description_pre_transit: Carrier vakatanga kuona zvemahwevhu nezvemapeci, asi haisundirwi uye haisati yadzokwa.
description_delivery_in_progress: Haisati yavakufika kune dzimwe dzakadoka nenguva yekushandiswa rinopfuura.
description_in_transit: Haisati yavakuda kuenda kuhwanda hwayo. Mukana ngaaronge uye munenge muchaita vhidhiyo mudzimba reiyo refu pekugara.
description_customs_clearance: Mapeki ako ari kufambiswa nekudzivirira. Kana panoda, unogona kubatana kune hunyanzvi, zvinyorwa kana kuti unoda kuwedzera zvemabvisero/mabhazi. Zvinoita kuti muzana zvinogadzirwa nekughamuchira zvisingagoneza zvakanaka.
description_return_to_sender: Haisati yakanyarara uye haisati yatanga kusvika kune atengeri.
description_expired: Haisati yakavenga nepanyaya yekutsigira panguva dzakareva 30 tangu yakatongwa.
description_transit_limit_exceeded: Haisati yakakanganiswa mukati menyu retime inopfuura. Ndapota dzokerai kune carrier.
description_unsuccessful_delivery: Carrier yakatsvaga kuti yadzoserwa, asi yakatsinzinya uye inototanga kugara nekurambidza ndokupindira toyenda yemusi.
description_error: Haikwani kugadzira pachipangano peyi mounenge usingagone kuirekodha. Ndapota ungatiziretse.
description_exception: Kuuya nehuwandu hwakawanda kana hwune hunyanzvi. Ndapota dzokerai kune carrier.
